o\": 741}, {\"ngram\": \"Glynis Walsh\", \"from\": 764, \"to\": 776}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Amid her own heartbreak, it was a generous gesture that lifted everyone.\", \"from\": 783, \"to\": 855, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her own heartbreak\", \"from\": 788, \"to\": 806}, {\"ngram\": \"a generous gesture\", \"from\": 815, \"to\": 833}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 854}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And then the following month she felt conflicted while sitting at home in Nashville, watching Alex swim in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 969, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 930, \"end\": 939, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nashville_Predators\", \"score\": 0.9999986205094011, \"rank\": 1.3794923690407578e-06, \"text\": \"Nashville\", \"types\": [\"Q4498974\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nashville_Predators\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nashville_Predators\"}, {\"begin\": 950, \"end\": 954, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"score\": 0.999918357546077, \"rank\": 7.998391974027073e-05, \"text\": \"Alex\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\"}, {\"begin\": 963, \"end\": 968, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999998118064646, \"rank\": 1.8420242706220008e-07, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 922, \"to\": 926}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWe had a camera crew from the local news, and it was really exciting and it was kind of like a production,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d she says.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009dIn that moment I could not really think about myself or whatever, but I was so upset not to be there.\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 1197, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWe\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 976}, {\"ngram\": \"a camera crew\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 994}, {\"ngram\": \"the local news\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1014}, {\"ngram\": \"a production\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1079}, {\"ngram\": \"whatever\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1160}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I wanted to watch her in person, and I wanted to be there swimming.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Last month at Olympic trials in Indianapolis, the roles were somewhat reversed.\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1349, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1302, \"end\": 1314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis\", \"score\": 0.9999999891560948, \"rank\": 1.079120142253469e-08, \"text\": \"Indianapolis\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"person\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1229}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic trials\", \"from\": 1283, \"to\": 1297}, {\"ngram\": \"the roles\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1324}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gretchen, age 21, made the U.S. team on the second day of the meet, after setting a world record in the 100 butterfly.\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1468, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"age\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1363}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S. team\", \"from\": 1373, \"to\": 1386}, {\"ngram\": \"the second day\", \"from\": 1390, \"to\": 1404}, {\"ngram\": \"the meet\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1416}, {\"ngram\": \"a world record\", \"from\": 1432, \"to\": 1446}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100 butterfly\", \"from\": 1450, \"to\": 1467}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then it took a few nerve-wracking days before Alex, age 22, joined her by making the team in the 200 IM again.\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1579, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1515, \"end\": 1519, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"score\": 0.999918357546077, \"rank\": 7.998391974