from\": 1702, \"to\": 1793, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1734, \"end\": 1739, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999998118064646, \"rank\": 1.8420242706220008e-07, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 1741, \"end\": 1745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"score\": 0.999918357546077, \"rank\": 7.998391974027073e-05, \"text\": \"Alex\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a silver medal\", \"from\": 1716, \"to\": 1730}, {\"ngram\": \"a prime medal contender\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1778}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200 IM\", \"from\": 1782, \"to\": 1792}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And Gretchen has broken through, tapping into her prodigious talents to make the U.S. team in the 100 butterfly, 100 freestyle and 50 freestyle; she\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s a major relay factor as well.\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1976, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1798, \"end\": 1806, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gretchen_Walsh\", \"score\": 0.9999658440996189, \"rank\": 3.415706730402129e-05, \"text\": \"Gretchen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gretchen_Walsh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gretchen_Walsh\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her prodigious talents\", \"from\": 1840, \"to\": 1862}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S. team\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1884}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100 butterfly\", \"from\": 1888, \"to\": 1905}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Onthe first day of swimming in Parison Saturday night, Gretchen earned a silver medal as part of the 4X100 freestyle relay team, and affirmed her prowess in the 100 butterfly, setting an Olympic record with a time of 55.38. \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWe always tell each other that we are stronger together,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Alex says.\", \"from\": 1978, \"to\": 2276, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2033, \"end\": 2041, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gretchen_Walsh\", \"score\": 0.9999658440996189, \"rank\": 3.415706730402129e-05, \"text\": \"Gretchen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gretchen_Walsh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gretchen_Walsh\"}, {\"begin\": 2266, \"end\": 2270, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"score\": 0.999918357546077, \"rank\": 7.998391974027073e-05, \"text\": \"Alex\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Parison\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2016}, {\"ngram\": \"a silver medal\", \"from\": 2049, \"to\": 2063}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2067, \"to\": 2071}, {\"ngram\": \"the 4X100 freestyle relay team\", \"from\": 2075, \"to\": 2105}, {\"ngram\": \"her prowess\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2131}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100 butterfly\", \"from\": 2135, \"to\": 2152}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic record\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2179}, {\"ngram\": \"a time\", \"from\": 2185, \"to\": 2191}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWe\", \"from\": 2202, \"to\": 2207}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cAnd that's been a really big game-changer for me because I definitely draw a lot of my confidence from Gretchen.\", \"from\": 2277, \"to\": 2392, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2383, \"end\": 2391, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gretchen_Walsh\", \"score\": 0.9999658440996189, \"rank\": 3.415706730402129e-05, \"text\": \"Gretchen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gretchen_Walsh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gretchen_Walsh\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cAnd\", \"from\": 2277, \"to\": 2283}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2355, \"to\": 2360}, {\"ngram\": \"my confidence\", \"from\": 2364, \"to\": 2377}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I would say just seeing her be poised and kind of manage this comeback that she's had after 2021, I gained a lot of confidence from that, and a lot of motivation.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Says Gretchen: \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt is a little bit of a different perspective from me as the younger sister.\", \"from\": 2393, \"to\": 2654, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2565, \"end\": 2573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gretchen_Walsh\", \"score\": 0.9999658440996189, \"rank\": 3.415706730402129e-05, \"text\": \"Gretchen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gretchen_Walsh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gretchen_Walsh\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this comeback\", \"from\": 2450, \"to\": 2463}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2500, \"to\": 2505}, {\"ngram\": \"confidence\", \"from\": 2509, \"to\": 2519}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2535, \"to\": 2540}, {\"ngram\": \"motivation.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 2544, \"to\": 2558}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt\", \"from\": 2574, \"to\": 2579}, {\"ngram\": \"a little bit\", \"from\": 2583, \"to\": 2595}, {\"ngram\": \"a different perspective\", \"from\": 2599, \"to\": 2622}, {\"ngram\": \"the younger sister\", \"from\": 2634, \"to\": 2652}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She is an amazing role model, but that comes with her kind of putting up a brave face.\", \"from\": 2655, \"to\": 2741, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an amazing role model\", \"from\": 2662, \"to\": 2683}, {\"ngram\": \"her kind\", \"from\": 2705, \"to\": 2713}, {\"ngram\": \"a brave face\", \"from\": 2728, \"to\": 2740}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I think sometimes as a younger sister, I do not see [Alex] struggle as much, but I feel like we support each other really, really well.\", \"from\": 2742, \"to\": 2880, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a younger sister\", \"from\": 2766, \"to\": 2782}, {\"ngram\": \"[Alex] struggle\", \"from\": 2797, \"to\": 2812}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Most of the time, especially now that we are quite a bit older, I definitely feel like I am totally transparent with Alex as to how I am feeling, and she's transparent with me as well.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Sunday night, Gretchen will take her first shot at an individual medal in the final of the 100 fly.\", \"from\": 2881, \"to\": 3169, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2998, \"end\": 3002, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"score\": 0.999918357546077, \"rank\": 7.998391974027073e-05, \"text\": \"Alex\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\"}, {\"begin\": 3084, \"end\": 3092, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gretchen_Walsh\", \"score\": 0.9999658440996189, \"rank\": 3.415706730402129e-05, \"text\": \"Gretchen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gretchen_Walsh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gretchen_Walsh\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 2889, \"to\": 2897}, {\"ngram\": \"well.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Sunday night\", \"from\": 3060, \"to\": 3081}, {\"ngram\": \"her first shot\", \"from\": 3102, \"to\": 3116}, {\"ngram\": \"an individual medal\", \"from\": 3120, \"to\": 3139}, {\"ngram\": \"the final\", \"from\": 3143, \"to\": 3152}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100 fly\", \"from\": 3156, \"to\": 3167}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her progress in that event has been breathtaking.\", \"from\": 3170, \"to\": 3219, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her progress\", \"from\": 3170, \"to\": 3182}, {\"ngram\": \"that event\", \"from\": 3186, \"to\": 3196}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2021 she finished 12th in a time of 58.46, not even making finals.\", \"from\": 3220, \"to\": 3289, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a time\", \"from\": 3249, \"to\": 3255}, {\"ngram\": \"finals\", \"from\": 3282, \"to\": 3288}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Three years later she smashed the world record with a time of 55.14.\", \"from\": 3290, \"to\": 3358, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world record\", \"from\": 3320, \"to\": 3336}, {\"ngram\": \"a time\", \"from\": 3342, \"to\": 3348}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gretchen heard the \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cbathtub swimmer\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d label that some hung on her a few years ago, when her performances in the long-course, 50-meter pool didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t measure up to what she did in the short-course, 25-yard pool.\", \"from\": 3360, \"to\": 3572, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gretchen\", \"from\": 3360, \"to\": 3368}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cbathtub swimmer\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d label\", \"from\": 3375, \"to\": 3406}, {\"ngram\": \"her performances\", \"from\": 3451, \"to\": 3467}, {\"ngram\": \"the long-course, 50-meter pool\", \"from\": 3471, \"to\": 3501}, {\"ngram\": \"the short-course, 25-yard pool\", \"from\": 3541, \"to\": 3571}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Hence the tub tag.)\", \"from\": 3573, \"to\": 3593, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"(Hence the tub tag\", \"from\": 3573, \"to\": 3591}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After setting four American short-course records during the college season and winning all seven events at NCAA championships, this summer served as the final validation that she could swim in the big pool, too.\", \"from\": 3594, \"to\": 3805, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3613, \"end\": 3621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9993386457558304, \"rank\": 0.0006609370407901707, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 3701, \"end\": 3705, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\", \"score\": 0.9999999999281499, \"rank\": 7.158724232288444e-11, \"text\": \"NCAA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the college season\", \"from\": 3650, \"to\": 3668}, {\"ngram\": \"all seven events\", \"from\": 3681, \"to\": 3697}, {\"ngram\": \"this summer\", \"from\": 3721, \"to\": 3732}, {\"ngram\": \"the final validation\", \"from\": 3743, \"to\": 3763}, {\"ngram\": \"the big pool\", \"from\": 3787, \"to\": 3799}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alex is an imposing 6-footer with plenty of athleticism, but Gretchen was always built like the ultimate swimming machine.\", \"from\": 3807, \"to\": 3929, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3807, \"end\": 3811, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"score\": 0.999918357546077, \"rank\": 7.998391974027073e-05, \"text\": \"Alex\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\"}, {\"begin\": 3868, \"end\": 3876, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gretchen_Walsh\", \"score\": 0.9999658440996189, \"rank\": 3.415706730402129e-05, \"text\": \"Gretchen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gretchen_Walsh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gretchen_Walsh\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an imposing 6-footer\", \"from\": 3815, \"to\": 3835}, {\"ngram\": \"plenty\", \"from\": 3841, \"to\": 3847}, {\"ngram\": \"athleticism\", \"from\": 3851, \"to\": 3862}, {\"ngram\": \"the ultimate swimming machine\", \"from\": 3899, \"to\": 3928}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s 6'3\\\", with the requisite long limbs to move large amounts of water.\", \"from\": 3930, \"to\": 4005, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"She\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 3930, \"to\": 3937}, {\"ngram\": \"the requisite long limbs\", \"from\": 3949, \"to\": 3973}, {\"ngram\": \"large amounts\", \"from\": 3982, \"to\": 3995}, {\"ngram\": \"water\", \"from\": 3999, \"to\": 4004}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But she\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s also double-jointed in her arms and legs\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094giving her an \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cuncanny flexibility,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d in the words of her coach at Virginia, Todd DeSorbo.\", \"from\": 4006, \"to\": 4154, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4131, \"end\": 4139, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Virginia_Cavaliers_football\", \"score\": 0.9999721994171513, \"rank\": 2.7331416573417857e-05, \"text\": \"Virginia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Virginia_Cavaliers_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Virginia_Cavaliers_football\"}, {\"begin\": 4141, \"end\": 4145, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Todd_Grimshaw\", \"score\": 0.5593792226087553, \"rank\": 0.7876958705527518, \"text\": \"Todd\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Todd_Grimshaw\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Todd_Grimshaw\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"she\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 4010, \"to\": 4017}, {\"ngram\": \"her arms\", \"from\": 4041, \"to\": 4049}, {\"ngram\": \"an \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cuncanny flexibility\", \"from\": 4072, \"to\": 4097}, {\"ngram\": \"the words\", \"from\": 4105, \"to\": 4114}, {\"ngram\": \"her coach\", \"from\": 4118, \"to\": 4127}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s a huge advantage.\", \"from\": 4155, \"to\": 4181, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 4155, \"to\": 4163}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are some crazy still photos of Gretchen swimming butterfly with her arms torquing at seemingly unnatural angles due to her double-jointed elbows.\", \"from\": 4183, \"to\": 4334, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4220, \"end\": 4228, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gretchen_Walsh\", \"score\": 0.9999658440996189, \"rank\": 3.415706730402129e-05, \"text\": \"Gretchen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gretchen_Walsh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gretchen_Walsh\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some crazy still photos\", \"from\": 4193, \"to\": 4216}, {\"ngram\": \"her arms torquing\", \"from\": 4253, \"to\": 4270}, {\"ngram\": \"seemingly unnatural angles\", \"from\": 4274, \"to\": 4300}, {\"ngram\": \"her double-jointed elbows\", \"from\": 4308, \"to\": 4333}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the bigger advantage comes from her ability to hyperextend her knees to get greater range of kicking motion underwater.\", \"from\": 4335, \"to\": 4458, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the bigger advantage\", \"from\": 4339, \"to\": 4359}, {\"ngram\": \"her ability\", \"from\": 4371, \"to\": 4382}, {\"ngram\": \"her knees\", \"from\": 4398, \"to\": 4407}, {\"ngram\": \"greater range\", \"from\": 4415, \"to\": 4428}, {\"ngram\": \"motion\", \"from\": 4440, \"to\": 4446}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cHer feet will travel further because her knees can bend backward,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d says Russell Mark of the American Swim Coaches Association, who studies and measures stroke efficiency.\", \"from\": 4460, \"to\": 4635, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4537, \"end\": 4549, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russell_Mark\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Russell Mark\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russell_Mark\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russell_Mark\"}, {\"begin\": 4557, \"end\": 4565, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9993386457558304, \"rank\": 0.0006609370407901707, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cHer feet\", \"from\": 4460, \"to\": 4471}, {\"ngram\": \"her knees\", \"from\": 4500, \"to\": 4509}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cShe has superior range of motion and mobility.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Gretchen\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s performance in Paris will play a significant part in whether the U.S. can top the medal table.\", \"from\": 4636, \"to\": 4797, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4718, \"end\": 4723, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999863576, \"rank\": 1.3289274901259008e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cShe\", \"from\": 4636, \"to\": 4642}, {\"ngram\": \"superior range\", \"from\": 4647, \"to\": 4661}, {\"ngram\": \"motion\", \"from\": 4665, \"to\": 4671}, {\"ngram\": \"performance\", \"from\": 4702, \"to\": 4713}, {\"ngram\": \"a significant part\", \"from\": 4733, \"to\": 4751}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 4763, \"to\": 4771}, {\"ngram\": \"the medal table\", \"from\": 4780, \"to\": 4795}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Alex will have a role in that as well, trying alongside Virginia teammate Kate Douglass to take down Australian Kaylee McKeown and Canadian Summer McIntosh in a loaded 200 IM.\", \"from\": 4798, \"to\": 4977, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4802, \"end\": 4806, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"score\": 0.999918357546077, \"rank\": 7.998391974027073e-05, \"text\": \"Alex\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\"}, {\"begin\": 4858, \"end\": 4866, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Virginia_Cavaliers_football\", \"score\": 0.9999721994171513, \"rank\": 2.7331416573417857e-05, \"text\": \"Virginia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Virginia_Cavaliers_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Virginia_Cavaliers_football\"}, {\"begin\": 4876, \"end\": 4889, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Douglass\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kate Douglass\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Douglass\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Douglass\"}, {\"begin\": 4903, \"end\": 4913, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9999999889614629, \"rank\": 1.0057396764482747e-08, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a role\", \"from\": 4817, \"to\": 4823}, {\"ngram\": \"Canadian Summer McIntosh\", \"from\": 4933, \"to\": 4957}, {\"ngram\": \"a loaded 200 IM\", \"from\": 4961, \"to\": 4976}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As much as anyone should ever plan on the moon shot of their children becoming Olympians, the Walshes could at least dream about it (times two) from a young age.\", \"from\": 4979, \"to\": 5140, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 4990, \"to\": 4996}, {\"ngram\": \"the moon shot\", \"from\": 5017, \"to\": 5030}, {\"ngram\": \"their children\", \"from\": 5034, \"to\": 5048}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympians\", \"from\": 5058, \"to\": 5067}, {\"ngram\": \"the Walshes\", \"from\": 5069, \"to\": 5080}, {\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 5112, \"to\": 5117}, {\"ngram\": \"a young age\", \"from\": 5128, \"to\": 5139}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Glynis Walsh had a modest swimming career at Boston College (then went on to medical school and is now an emergency-medicine physician), and she and Robert got the kids in the water early.\", \"from\": 5141, \"to\": 5329, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5186, \"end\": 5200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_College\", \"score\": 0.9978999295351361, \"rank\": 0.002104485210144, \"text\": \"Boston College\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_College\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_College\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Glynis Walsh\", \"from\": 5141, \"to\": 5153}, {\"ngram\": \"a modest swimming career\", \"from\": 5158, \"to\": 5182}, {\"ngram\": \"medical school\", \"from\": 5218, \"to\": 5232}, {\"ngram\": \"an emergency-medicine physician\", \"from\": 5244, \"to\": 5275}, {\"ngram\": \"Robert\", \"from\": 5290, \"to\": 5296}, {\"ngram\": \"the kids\", \"from\": 5301, \"to\": 5309}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 5313, \"to\": 5322}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although Gretchen announced after a race at age 6 that she was quitting the sport because the water was too cold, she and Alex progressed rapidly through the ranks at young ages.\", \"from\": 5331, \"to\": 5509, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5340, \"end\": 5348, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gretchen_Walsh\", \"score\": 0.9999658440996189, \"rank\": 3.415706730402129e-05, \"text\": \"Gretchen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gretchen_Walsh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gretchen_Walsh\"}, {\"begin\": 5453, \"end\": 5457, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"score\": 0.999918357546077, \"rank\": 7.998391974027073e-05, \"text\": \"Alex\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a race\", \"from\": 5365, \"to\": 5371}, {\"ngram\": \"age\", \"from\": 5375, \"to\": 5378}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 5403, \"to\": 5412}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 5421, \"to\": 5430}, {\"ngram\": \"the ranks\", \"from\": 5485, \"to\": 5494}, {\"ngram\": \"young ages\", \"from\": 5498, \"to\": 5508}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At one point when the girls were in grade school, Robert\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094who was a high-school basketball player\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094had them do a local tryout for a team in that sport.\", \"from\": 5510, \"to\": 5663, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one point\", \"from\": 5513, \"to\": 5522}, {\"ngram\": \"the girls\", \"from\": 5528, \"to\": 5537}, {\"ngram\": \"grade school\", \"from\": 5546, \"to\": 5558}, {\"ngram\": \"Robert\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094who\", \"from\": 5560, \"to\": 5572}, {\"ngram\": \"a high-school basketball player\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094had\", \"from\": 5577, \"to\": 5614}, {\"ngram\": \"a local tryout\", \"from\": 5623, \"to\": 5637}, {\"ngram\": \"a team\", \"from\": 5642, \"to\": 5648}, {\"ngram\": \"that sport\", \"from\": 5652, \"to\": 5662}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThey did incredibly well,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Robert recalls.\", \"from\": 5665, \"to\": 5712, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThey\", \"from\": 5665, \"to\": 5672}, {\"ngram\": \"Robert\", \"from\": 5697, \"to\": 5703}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cAnd we walked out of the gym and I said, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0098That went great.\", \"from\": 5713, \"to\": 5776, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the gym\", \"from\": 5737, \"to\": 5744}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0098That\", \"from\": 5757, \"to\": 5764}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's one game a week and one practice.\", \"from\": 5777, \"to\": 5815, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one game\", \"from\": 5782, \"to\": 5790}, {\"ngram\": \"one practice\", \"from\": 5802, \"to\": 5814}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This would be so much fun.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 And they both laughe